# RGL: 3D plot example
Jesse Leigh Patsolic  
`r Sys.Date()`  



## Generate toy data

```r
set.seed(2357)
n <- 500
dat <- data.frame(x = runif(n), 
                  y = rnorm(n),
                  z=rpois(n,lambda=3),
                  col=rbinom(n,size=4,prob=c(1:4)/4))
```


```r
rgl::plot3d(dat$x,dat$y,dat$z,type='s',size=1,col=dat$col+1)
subid <- currentSubscene3d()
rglwidget(elementId="3d",width=720,height=720)
```
